 City|Quebec City, QC]])\n|'''[[Winnipeg Wesmen]]'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|1994\n|[[University of Winnipeg|Winnipeg]]<br>([[Winnipeg|Winnipeg, MB]])\n|'''[[Calgary Dinos]]'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Winnipeg Wesmen]]\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|8\n|- \n|1995\n|[[University of Alberta|Alberta]]<br>([[Edmonton|Edmonton, AB]])\n|'''[[Alberta Pandas]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Winnipeg Wesmen]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|1996\n|[[University of Toronto|Toronto]]<br>([[Toronto|Toronto, ON]])\n|'''[[Alberta Pandas]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Winnipeg Wesmen]]\n|8\n|- \n|1997\n|[[University of Alberta|Alberta]]<br>([[Edmonton|Edmonton, AB]])\n|'''[[Alberta Pandas]]'''\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|1998\n|[[University of Alberta|Alberta]]<br>([[Edmonton|Edmonton, AB]])\n|'''[[Alberta Pandas]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|8\n|- \n|1999\n|[[University of Alberta|Alberta]]<br>([[Edmonton|Edmonton, AB]])\n|'''[[Alberta Pandas]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2000\n|[[University of Winnipeg|Winnipeg]]<br>([[Winnipeg|Winnipeg, MB]])\n|'''[[Alberta Pandas]]'''\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|8\n|- \n|2001\n|[[University of Manitoba|Manitoba]]<br>([[Winnipeg|Winnipeg, MB]])\n|'''[[Manitoba Bisons]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Sherbrooke Vert et Or]]\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Toronto Varsity Blues]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2002\n|[[Universit\u00e9 Laval|Laval]]<br>([[Quebec City|Quebec City, QC]])\n|'''[[Manitoba Bisons]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Sherbrooke Vert et Or]]\n|8\n|-\n|2003\n|[[Universit\u00e9 Laval|Laval]]<br>([[Quebec City|Quebec City, QC]])\n|'''[[Sherbrooke Vert et Or]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Winnipeg Wesmen]]\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2004\n|[[University of Saskatchewan|Saskatchewan]]<br>([[Saskatoon|Saskatoon, SK]])\n|'''[[Calgary Dinos]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|8\n|-\n|2005\n|[[University of Saskatchewan|Saskatchewan]]<br>([[Saskatoon|Saskatoon, SK]])\n|'''[[Sherbrooke Vert et Or]]'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2006\n|[[University of Calgary|Calgary]]<br>([[Calgary|Calgary, AB]])\n|'''[[Laval Rouge et Or]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|8\n|-\n|2007\n|[[University of Calgary|Calgary]]<br>([[Calgary|Calgary, AB]])\n|'''[[Alberta Pandas]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Trinity Western Spartans]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2008\n|[[University of New Brunswick|New Brunswick]]<br>([[Fredericton|Fredericton, NB]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|8\n|-\n|2009<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2009-10/boxscores/20100307_0mq5.xml Details]\n|[[University of New Brunswick|New Brunswick]]<br>([[Fredericton|Fredericton, NB]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2010<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2009-10/boxscores/20100307_0mq5.xml Details]\n|[[University of Alberta|Alberta]]<br>([[Edmonton|Edmonton, AB]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Manitoba Bisons]]\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|8\n|-\n|2011<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2010-11/releases/20110306-final Details]\n|[[Universit\u00e9 Laval|Laval]]<br>([[Quebec City|Quebec City, QC]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|[[Trinity Western Spartans]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2012<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2011-12/releases/20120304-final Details]\n|[[McMaster University|McMaster]]<br>([[Hamilton, Ontario|Hamilton, ON]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|[[McGill Martlets]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|8\n|-\n|2013<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2013/releases/final Details]\n|[[Universit\u00e9 de Sherbrooke|Sherbrooke]]<br>([[Sherbrooke|Sherbrooke, QC]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|[[Trinity Western Spartans]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Ottawa Gee-Gees]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2014<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2014/releases/final Details]\n|[[University of Regina|Regina]]<br>([[Regina, Saskatchewan|Regina, SK]])\n|'''[[Manitoba Bisons]]'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|[[Laval Rouge et Or]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Dalhousie Tigers]]\n|8\n|-\n|2015<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2015/releases/final Details]\n|[[University of Toronto|Toronto]]<br>([[Toronto|Toronto, ON]])\n|'''[[Trinity Western Spartans]]'''\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Toronto Varsity Blues]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2016<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2016/releases/final Details]\n|[[Brandon University|Brandon]]<br>([[Brandon, Manitoba|Brandon, MB]])\n|'''[[Toronto Varsity Blues]]'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[Trinity Western Spartans]]\n|[[UBC Okanagan Heat]]\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|8\n|-\n|2017<br>[https://presto-en.usports.ca/championships/wvball/2017/releases/final Details]\n|[[Ryerson University|Ryerson]]<br>([[Toronto|Toronto, ON]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|[[Trinity Western Spartans]]\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Montreal Carabins]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2018<br>[https://usports.ca/en/championships/volleyball/f/news/2018/03/3040019754/final Details]\n|[[Universit\u00e9 Laval|Laval]]<br>([[Quebec City|Quebec City, QC]])\n|'''[[Ryerson Rams]]'''\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|[[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n|'''3\u20131'''\n|[[Calgary Dinos]]\n|8\n|- \n|2019<br>[https://usports.ca/en/championships/volleyball/f/news/2019/03/2230475171/final Details]\n|[[University of Alberta|Alberta]]<br>([[Edmonton|Edmonton, AB]])\n|'''[[UBC Thunderbirds]]'''\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Ryerson Rams]]\n|[[Alberta Pandas]]\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|[[Dalhousie Tigers]]\n|8\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2020\n|[[University of Calgary|Calgary]]<br>([[Calgary|Calgary, AB]])\n|colspan=3|''Cancelled ([[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]])''<ref name=corona/>\n|colspan=3|''Cancelled ([[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]])''<ref name=corona/>\n|8\n|- \n|2021\n|[[University of British Columbia|British Columbia]]<br>([[Vancouver|Vancouver, BC]])\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|8\n|-\n|}\n<ref name=\"U Sports history\"/><ref name=\"Archive\"/>\n\n==Top 3 finishes table==\nDue to information limitations, the following table includes all known first, second, and third place finishes, as indicated above. Prior to 1983, there were no third place finishes, and the second place finish was the loser of the championship game.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"  style=\"font-size: 90%\"\n|-\n! Team\n! Conference\n! 1st\n! 2nd\n! 3rd\n! {{abbr|Last|Last championship win}}\n|-\n| [[UBC Thunderbirds]]\n| [[Canada West Universities Athletic Association|Canada W